headline: Game On! GoDaddy Returns to Super Bowl Advertising
summary: Aspiring small business owners struggling to turn their ideas into reality should tune into Super Bowl LIX to learn how GoDaddy Airo uses the power of artificial intelligence (AI) to take a business from concept to online in minutes.
